              <p><b>To ensure a fair comparison, Star Ratings only appear when there is enough relevant historical data for the runners in a race.</b></p>
              <p>Not all data points are relevant for every race. Star Ratings takes this into account and will only highlight relevant data points that apply to this race.</p>
                <p>For example, Star Ratings will not highlight exceptional statistic on a Firm Track if the race is being run on a Heavy Track. </p>
                <p>This same concept applies to:</p>
